snippet: Russia's anti-doping agency RUSADA said on Wednesday it had not admitted to mass doping in the country's sports system and that a report in the New York Times which suggested it had was a distortion of its position....
lead_paragraph: Russia's anti-doping agency RUSADA said on Wednesday it had not admitted to mass doping in the country's sports system and that a report in the New York Times which suggested it had was a distortion of its position.

headline.main: Russia's Anti-Doping Body Says Did Not Admit to Sports Dope Conspiracy
headline.print_headline: Russia's Anti-Doping Body Says Did Not Admit to Sports Dope Conspiracy
